featured_reviews.review_id:
More than 150 Men can pray at this mosque,
There is seperate prayer hall  for ladies ,more than 10 ladies can pray,
Efficient water service,
Separate 2 rest rooms for ladies,
Very useful for highway travellers,especially for those r with families,
Very big parking facility,
You will enjoy this place Pleasantly
Very Good atmosphere,
Best environment around the mosque,
There is no conditions for separate jamath prayers,
You can pray as per hadith and quranic way!

Don't park your vehicles outside the mosque, its the very dangerous road junction.
Park ur vehicles inside the mosque.
Hope this comment will useful to you!
